Bose Omolayo (amụrụ ya n'ụbọchị mbụ n'ọnwa Febụwarị n'afọ 1989) bụ onye Naịjirịa na-eme egwuregwu ibu ike nke a na-akpọ Powerlifter n'olu bekeee. O riitere ọla edo na ihe omume ụmụ nwanyị 79 kilogram n'afọ 2020 na Summer Paralympics nke emere na Tokyo, Japan. Mgbe ọnwa ole na ole gachara, o ritere ọla edo na ihe omume ya n'afọ 2021 World Para Powerlifting Championships nke emere na Tbilisi, Georgia. N'ihe omume a, o setịpụkwara ihe ndekọ ụwa ọhụrụ nke kilogram 144.
O sonyere na asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị +61 kilogram na 2014 Commonwealth Games ebe o ritere ihe nrite ọlaọcha.
